<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 21:14:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西尔弗表示，在争议之后他预计NBA比赛将重返中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</link><description>亚当·萧华 (Adam Silver) 专员认为，在香港民主抗议引发的争议引发对北美顶级联赛的强烈抵制五年后，NBA 可能会再次在中国举办比赛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/silver-says-he-expects-nba-games-will-return-china-after-controversy-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普以汽车贷款税收减免和中国镇压来吸引汽车工人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周四提议对汽车贷款利息实行免税，并阻止中国汽车制造商在美国销售汽车，以期在竞选活动的最后几周吸引汽车工人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-propose-making-car-loan-interest-tax-deductible-speech-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>世界杯预选赛日本队击败沙特阿拉伯队保持完美</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-down-jordan-remain-unbeaten-world-cup-qualifying-2024-10-10/</link><description>周四，日本在吉达以 2-0 击败沙特阿拉伯，守保肇的球队在亚洲区预选赛中取得三连胜，继续向世界杯进军，这使得武士蓝在 C 组领先 5 分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-down-jordan-remain-unbeaten-world-cup-qualifying-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称“核五国”即将在纽约举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-nuclear-five-states-meet-soon-new-york-2024-10-10/</link><description>俄罗斯官方媒体周四援引外交部副部长谢尔盖·里亚布科夫的话说，五个核武器国家小组将在未来两周内在纽约举行会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 15:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-nuclear-five-states-meet-soon-new-york-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称四名富士康员工在中国被拘留</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-four-foxconn-employees-detained-china-2024-10-10/</link><description>台湾政府表示，全球最大的 iPhone 组装商台湾富士康的四名员工在中国被拘留，情况“相当奇怪”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-four-foxconn-employees-detained-china-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫否认朝鲜士兵在乌克兰作战的报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-dismisses-reports-north-korean-soldiers-fighting-ukraine-2024-10-10/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四驳回了韩国的说法，即朝鲜可能已派遣一些军事人员帮助俄罗斯对抗乌克兰，并可能正在考虑进行更大规模的部署。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:31:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-dismisses-reports-north-korean-soldiers-fighting-ukraine-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚3-1战胜中国开启波波维奇时代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</link><description>周四，托尼·波波维奇作为澳大利亚队主教练在阿德莱德椭圆形球场举行的世界杯预选赛中以 3-1 战胜中国队，取得了胜利的开局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>宜家呼吁中国采取更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</link><description>在中国政府宣布一揽子措施以重振遭受房地产危机打击的经济后，瑞典家具零售商宜家周四敦促中国采取进一步的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>房地产市场疲软降价后宜家销售额下降 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</link><description>瑞典廉价家居用品零售商宜家为了吸引更多购物者并维持其在不断萎缩的家居市场中的份额而降价，该公司的年销售额下降了 5%，但预计明年将出现复苏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>莱尼将向德国政府提交中国股权出售案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</link><description>汽车供应商莱尼 (Leoni) 发言人周四表示，该公司正准备向德国政府登记将其多数股权出售给中国公司立讯精密 (Luxshare)，这被称为例行步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行原副行长因受贿被判死刑缓期执行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</link><description>官方媒体周四称，在金融业开展全面反腐运动之际，中国前央行副行长范一飞因受贿罪被判处死刑，缓期两年执行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国将于年底前取消对澳大利亚龙虾的进口禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周四表示，中国将在年底前恢复进口澳大利亚龙虾，这标志着长达四年的外交斗争的结束，这场斗争导致澳大利亚数百亿美元的出口被禁止进入中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着全球需求降温，中国九月出口可能进一步放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</link><description>9月份中国出口增速可能为五个月来最慢，这表明制造商不再在几个贸易伙伴征收关税之前急于发出订单，而且全球对中国商品的需求正在疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>袭击发生后中国将与巴基斯坦合作保护中国人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</link><description>周日，一个分裂主义武装组织声称杀害了两名中国工程师，中国周四表示，将与巴基斯坦合作，保护在巴基斯坦的中国人员、项目和机构的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国奇瑞在西方竞争对手腾出的俄罗斯工厂组装汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</link><description>自入侵乌克兰以来，北京在俄罗斯不断变化的制造业格局和经济中发挥着越来越有影响力的作用。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>